{"type":"message","id":"dc1edf03","parentId":"4b21c235","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:51:22.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I got the real-time data. Now I need to filter by alert rules and send alerts. Let me read the realtime-data.txt to see the data, then create a script to filter and send alerts.\n\nLooking at the alert rules:\n- Generic: drop > 3% or rise > 5%\n- 中国石油 (601857.SH): rise > 2% or drop > 1%\n\nFrom the data I can see:\n- 601857 中国石油: -2.85% - This triggers the 中国石油专属规则 (drop > 1%)\n- 601069 西部黄金: -2.85% - This doesn't trigger generic rule (needs > 3% drop)\n\nLet me check the data file and then filter it properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d9d3e55e72b642fca4c1668b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773121878839}}
{"type":"message","id":"2400b8ee","parentId":"dc1edf03","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:51:22.672Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d9d3e55e72b642fca4c1668b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码 | 名称 | 现价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间\n000975|山金国际|¥32.49|-1.22%|¥-0.40|2026-03-10 13:51:17\n601899|紫金矿业|¥36.98|-1.49%|¥-0.56|2026-03-10 13:51:17\n000852|石化机械|¥8.09|-1.58%|¥-0.13|2026-03-10 13:51:15\n600256|广汇能源|¥6.72|-1.61%|¥-0.11|2026-03-10 13:51:14\n688111|金山办公|¥285.72|-1.68%|¥-4.87|2026-03-10 13:51:18\n601808|中海油服|¥17.90|-1.76%|¥-0.32|2026-03-10 13:51:14\n600547|山东黄金|¥47.07|-1.86%|¥-0.89|2026-03-10 13:51:15\n600988|赤峰黄金|¥40.58|-1.96%|¥-0.81|2026-03-10 13:51:16\n600583|海油工程|¥7.19|-2.18%|¥-0.16|2026-03-10 13:51:15\n002716|湖南白银|¥15.07|-2.40%|¥-0.37|2026-03-10 13:51:17\n601069|西部黄金|¥37.56|-2.85%|¥-1.10|2026-03-10 13:51:16\n601857|中国石油|¥11.95|-2.85%|¥-0.35|2026-03-10 13:51:14\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773121882670}}
{"type":"message","id":"a31c3936","parentId":"2400b8ee","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:51:39.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to filter by alert rules:\n- Generic: drop > 3% or rise > 5% → No stocks match this\n- 中国石油 (601857.SH): rise > 2% or drop > 1% → 中国石油 is at -2.85%, which is a drop > 1%, so it triggers!\n\nSo 中国石油 should trigger an alert. Let me create a script to filter and generate the alert message, then send it via Feishu.\n\nActually, looking at the data more carefully:\n- 601857 中国石油: -2.85% → This is a drop of 2.85%, which is > 1%, so it triggers the 中国石油专属规则\n\nLet me create a filter script and then send the alert.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_06a0b8f235b244128028a1ca","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/filter-alerts.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nFilter realtime data by alert rules and output alert results\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nREALTIME_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\")\nALERT_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-results.txt\")\n\ndef check_alert_rules(code, name, pct_chg):\n    \"\"\"Check if stock triggers alert rules\"\"\"\n    # Generic rules: drop > 3% or rise > 5%\n    if pct_chg > 5.0:\n        return True, \"通用规则 (涨>5%)\"\n    if pct_chg < -3.0:\n        return True, \"通用规则 (跌>3%)\"\n    \n    # 中国石油 special rules: rise > 2% or drop > 1%\n    if code == '601857' or '中国石油' in name:\n        if pct_chg > 2.0:\n            return True, \"中国石油专属规则 (涨>2%)\"\n        if pct_chg < -1.0:\n            return True, \"中国石油专属规则 (跌>1%)\"\n    \n    return False, None\n\ndef main():\n    print(f\"🔍 开始过滤预警数据 - {datetime.now()}\")\n    \n    alert_results = []\n    \n    if os.path.exists(REALTIME_FILE):\n        with open(REALTIME_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            lines = f.readlines()\n        \n        # Skip header\n        for line in lines[1:]:\n            line = line.strip()\n            if not line:\n                continue\n            \n            parts = line.split('|')\n            if len(parts) >= 5:\n                code = parts[0]\n                name = parts[1]\n                price_str = parts[2].replace('¥', '')\n                pct_str = parts[3].replace('%', '')\n                \n                try:\n                    price = float(price_str)\n                    pct_chg = float(pct_str)\n                except:\n                    continue\n                \n                triggered, rule = check_alert_rules(code, name, pct_chg)\n                if triggered:\n                    alert_results.append({\n                        'code': code,\n                        'name': name,\n                        'price': price,\n                        'pct_chg': pct_chg,\n                        'rule': rule,\n                        'time': parts[5] if len(parts) > 5 else datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n                    })\n    \n    # Write alert results\n    with open(ALERT_FILE, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(\"代码 | 名称 | 现价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 触发规则 | 时间\\n\")\n        for r in sorted(alert_results, key=lambda x: x['pct_chg'], reverse=True):\n            price_change = r['price'] * r['pct_chg'] / 100\n            f.write(f\"{r['code']}|{r['name']}|¥{r['price']:.2f}|{r['pct_chg']:+.2f}%|¥{price_change:.2f}|{r['rule']}|{r['time']}\\n\")\n    \n    if alert_results:\n        print(f\"⚠️ {len(alert_results)} 只股票触发预警:\")\n        for r in alert_results:\n            change_symbol = \"🔴\" if r['pct_chg'] >= 0 else \"🟢\"\n            print(f\"  {r['code']} {r['name']}: ¥{r['price']:.2f} ({r['pct_chg']:+.2f}%) {change_symbol} - {r['rule']}\")\n        print(f\"📁 预警数据保存至：{ALERT_FILE}\")\n    else:\n        print(\"✅ 无股票触发预警规则\")\n    \n    # Output for message sending\n    if alert_results:\n        print(\"\\n=== 预警消息内容 ===\")\n        msg_lines = [\"⚠️ 股价预警通知\", f\"时间：{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\", \"\"]\n        msg_lines.append(\"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 触发规则 |\")\n        msg_lines.append(\"|------|------|--------|--------|----------|\")\n        for r in sorted(alert_results, key=lambda x: x['pct_chg'], reverse=True):\n            change_symbol = \"🔴\" if r['pct_chg'] >= 0 else \"🟢\"\n            msg_lines.append(f\"| {r['code']} | {r['name']} | ¥{r['price']:.2f} | {r['pct_chg']:+.2f}% {change_symbol} | {r['rule']} |\")\n        msg_lines.append(\"\")\n        msg_lines.append(\"⚙️ 预警规则\")\n        msg_lines.append(\"• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\")\n        msg_lines.append(\"• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\")\n        msg_lines.append(\"• 中国石油：涨>2% 或 跌>1% → 触发\")\n        \n        print('\\n'.join(msg_lines))\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773121882672}}
